<title>IRAN: Iran pardons over 1,000 prisoners.</title>
<headline>Iran pardons over 1,000 prisoners.</headline>
<dateline>TEHRAN 1997-07-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Iran will free or commute jail terms on 1,149 prisoners under a pardon approved by the Islamic republic's supreme leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, the official IRNA news agency reported on Tuesday.</p>
<p>It said the pardon, proposed by the head of the judiciary Mohammed Yazdi to mark the birth anniversary of Prophet Mohammad, covered prisoners sentenced by the Islamic revolutiuonary and military courts.</p>
<p>Iran will celebrate the birth of Prophet Mohammad on Wednesday.</p>
